OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Bankrupt' council leader  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fapologises to city         
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The leader of Birmingham City Council  
OL,6, has apologised to the people of the    
OL,7, city and insisted he had "no prior     
OL,8, notice" of its "bankruptcy" crisis.    
OL,10,FCouncillor John Cotton said he had met 
OL,11,Fwith Levelling Up secretary Michael    
OL,12,FGove this week to discuss support.     
OL,14,FThe leader was on holiday in the US    
OL,15,Fwhen the section 114 notice was issued,
OL,16,Fhalting all new spending.              
OL,18,FHe confirmed "all council activity" was
OL,19,Fbeing reviewed but pledged to protect  
OL,20,F"the things that matter most".         
